Dear Students,

We are planning for a  *Blood Donation Camp* in our college campus next week.

Every day, countless individuals rely on blood transfusions for their survival, be it due to medical emergencies, surgeries, or chronic illnesses. Unfortunately, there is an ongoing shortage of blood supply in our community, posing a significant challenge in meeting the needs of those in critical conditions.

By donating blood, you have the incredible power to give someone a second chance at life. Your generosity can alleviate the suffering of patients and bring hope to their families. It only takes a small amount of your time, but the impact you can make is immeasurable.

To send a invite to the concerned organization we need to know the count of interested people who can donate the blood. For the same kindly fill the form given in below link by tomorrow 12:30 PM.
https://forms.gle/9Qm2WBzx54bzVuba8

Looking forward to the kind cooperation.
Thanks

All the important details about the placement drive are given below:-

Brief Overview of the organization:-

Basiq360 is a comprehensive business automation platform designed to automate and digitize business operations. It helps companies help their sales force and channel partners close more deals faster with proper rewards, ensure authentic products get delivered in the right areas, and deploy QR-code based automation inside every processâ€”from sales to after-sales.

We are currently seeking candidates for the position ofÂ Software development and Project Coordinator of Basiq 360.Â We believe that our opening could be a great fit for individuals seeking a challenging andÂ rewarding career.Â 

We are hiringÂ for Technical and Management degrees both.(Fresher and Experience).Â Â The Candidate should onlyÂ be considered who is ready to complete the 2 years bond and do submit 10th marksheet (Original) on the very first day of joining along with all joining documents.Â
